  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 13</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 29 | <b>Successes:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 17 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 33</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, H, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This ultimate fire style technique calls forth the terrible power of Suzaku, the great phoenix, guardian of the South. Creatures in the area take your weapon damage, as well as 5d6 sonic and 5d6 fire damage (Reflex halves). Any creature suffering damage becomes @Condition[dazed;duration=1]{dazed} for 1 round (Fortitude negates). You take 7d6 damage when performing this technique.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the fire and sonic damage by 1d6 each, up to 1d6 per level or 20d6 total. Each additional die increases the damage you take by 1.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step allows you to take no damage when performing this technique.<br><br>The fifth step allows you to ignore the damage you would take when empowering this technique.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
